"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"在本期播客中，我们邀请到了六位小伙伴，一起探讨了Gamefi机制有关的话题。从玩法、Token设计、玩家收益等多维度分析了当下链游机制。 最近大火的GameFi就是Game + DeFi的组合，由于游戏天然具有娱乐和成瘾机制，因此,GameFi比DeFi更能吸引用户。我们以SkyWeaver, Town Star, StarAtlas,Axie Infinity, Aavegotchi, illuvium 这六款火爆链游为例展开讨论，如果你想了解一款好的GameFi具有哪些特性，包含哪些经济系统原理，相信在本期播客可以找到一些思路。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/0vQYWWY-tYKANNWHZQufB.jpg?height=720&width=1080)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641633714,\"title\":\"记录我听6个小伙伴解释6个GamFi机制\"},\"digest\":\"VhaWEsG9KjbN5IETMToE_-DyOQiXkQzW1SSd67zLd24\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x76893610339759eD198aB5ceD67eD4da902ABB64\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ofmfJ9GKa-7v-vCm85DsizHOgACTrwfm8nDiRDSbclA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"EBElAwdHvslyn2tFCPfEuYjBcQ8uWK3hVsQh4HaSH9k\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"RIy9nB3DtZoGtTdt0FHjKihKAVmPERowNpHUARmUP9w7PLn6OUqkljIp9aQHGNsFIXZkej6_HT3vQ3P7fvDsCQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x674378213d74e3b725622d4be665403c68671d680975ab1511c3410fe0ad8eca5f589d4ef65d2d48851685fc8eeea18b4000055fd2bc959a6228d61080d471b91c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ofmfJ9GKa-7v-vCm85DsizHOgACTrwfm8nDiRDSbclA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"EBElAwdHvslyn2tFCPfEuYjBcQ8uWK3hVsQh4HaSH9k\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"vf4_Cmv5utraBEQM8pcQ5pGk41iQvGxKi9rX6ugiz1s\"}"